# Full Stack Web Development Projects – Hex Softwares

This repository contains a collection of modern and responsive full stack web development projects developed during my internship at Hex Softwares. The purpose of this 
repository is to showcase practical implementation of frontend and backend technologies, UI/UX design skills, responsive layouts, API integrations, authentication systems, 
and complete web application development workflows.

## 🚀 Internship Role

**Full Stack Web Developer Intern**
at Hex Softwares

During this internship, I worked on designing and developing real-world web applications using modern web technologies. The projects focus on creating clean user interfaces,
responsive designs, dynamic functionality, and scalable backend systems.

---

# 📌 Technologies Used

## Frontend

* HTML5
* CSS3
* Bootstrap 5
* JavaScript (ES6)

## Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js

## Database

* MongoDB

## Additional Tools & Services

* JWT Authentication
* REST APIs
* Razorpay Integration (Test Mode)
* LocalStorage
* Git & GitHub

